&lt;p&gt;The team at Myticas Consulting is seeking a self-motivated &lt;strong&gt;Technical Analyst&lt;/strong&gt; to support a long-term engagement with our non for profit client. This is a 2-year contract opportunity ideal for a DevOps-savvy analyst with a strong foundation in system analysis and cloud/infrastructure operations. The ideal candidate will thrive in a collaborative environment, have a passion for automation and modern DevOps practices, and be eager to take ownership in a hands-on technical role.&lt;/p&gt;

