	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm 0.0cm 8.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Calibri , sans-serif;"&gt;In coordination with the Network and System Engineering teams attend, contribute and produce materials for internal and external design and system engineering reviews for Network Engineering related activities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
