&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;POSITION OVERVIEW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Engineering/Development Lead will oversee the development and delivery of our SaaS products, ensuring technical excellence and alignment with business objectives. This role requires hands-on involvement in both front-end and back-end development, guiding a team of engineers to build scalable and secure applications.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
