&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Description:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;The Project Manager will play a key role in leading and coordinating strategic security technology initiatives under the Global Security Project Management Office (PMO), ensuring effective execution and successful delivery across a portfolio of projects. The Project Manager must possess a strong understanding of project management best practices along with strong communication, influencing and stakeholder management skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;ul style="margin-bottom: 0.0cm;margin-top: 0.0cm;"&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Serve as project manager for multiple concurrent strategic projects.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Manage project intake, scheduling, timeline tracking, milestone management, and meeting facilitation as per GS PMO processes.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Draft and maintain project documentation (e.g., 4 ups), following up regularly with team members to ensure progress and accountability.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Arrange and facilitate regular stakeholder meetings.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Collect, document, and communicate project success metrics, key ownership details, and critical milestones with relevant teams.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Measure project outcomes and success against organizational goals.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Identify opportunities for process improvements and alignment, taking action as needed.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Develop and implement change management plans for integration of new projects and processes.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Create communications and support channels for upcoming changes, fostering user adoption and minimizing resistance.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Build and maintain long-term project timelines and RACI matrices to clarify roles and responsibilities.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Lead initiatives such as data standardization for systems like Genetec access control.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Ensure project governance, process documentation, and training resources are developed, stored, and shared as appropriate.&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;li style="margin: 0.0cm;font-size: 12.0pt;font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 11.0pt;"&gt;Confirm that systems and projects meet policy and training requirements.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
