&lt;span style="font-size: 10.0pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: Aptos , sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: white;"&gt;&lt;span style=""&gt;&lt;span style="color: rgb(33,37,41);"&gt;The Senior Cloud/DevOps Engineer leads the design, maintenance, transition to, and operations of cloud platforms. The Engineer collaborates with stakeholders to obtain and translate business requirements into technical implementations and provides guidance to technical teams regarding architectural and procedural best practices and functional experience. This position is considered advanced level and performs work of moderate to high complexity. The incumbent works under general supervision and may lead some efforts autonomously. This position does not have any direct reports but may lead or mentor of junior staff.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
