Clover Consulting (a Myticas Co.) is seeking an &lt;strong&gt;IT Plant Manager&lt;/strong&gt; for a large client in Orion, MI. This role is crucial in managing all IT-related activities at the local plant, with key responsibilities encompassing infrastructure, manufacturing software, and business operations. Local candidates are strongly preferred.&lt;br&gt;
