&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Title: &lt;/strong&gt;Cyber Posture Management Analyst&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Type: &lt;/strong&gt;Direct Hire&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;Lansing, Michigan&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Clover Consulting (a Myticas Co.) has a large, direct client seeking a skilled Cyber Posture Mgmt. Analyst I to join the team as part of their Information Security &amp; Privacy team. This position provides security analysis for the company's Identity and Access Management (IAM) Operation's program. This role requires knowledge across multiple platforms, applications, processes, and procedures to enable access management of business initiatives across the enterprise.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Essential Responsibilities&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
