&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Sr. Electrical Revit Designer&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Contract, 6+ mos. - up to $65/hour (flexible based on experience)&lt;br&gt;
Benefits: Standard Medical, Dental, and 401(k)&lt;br&gt;
In office: M- F&lt;br&gt;
